{"parentUuid":"4186cc6d-9da2-4ad4-81d9-945d6f9564cd","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"dcbe4efb-6e32-4db6-a75a-aa49b911d737","agentId":"ada254e2f5c7002a8","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01N9d89968HTX26UBGDpxjEC","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Qwen2.5-Coder technical report HumanEval LiveCodeBench 7B 14B 32B official scores\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Qwen2.5-Coder Technical Report\",\"url\":\"https://www.emergentmind.com/papers/2409.12186\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen2.5-Coder Technical Report\",\"url\":\"https://arxiv.org/html/2409.12186v3\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen2.5-Coder] LLM specialized for code generation, completion, and mathematical reasoning tasks | AI-SCHOLAR | AI: (Artificial Intelligence) Articles and technical information media\",\"url\":\"https://ai-scholar.tech/en/articles/large-language-models/Qwen2.5-Coder\"},{\"title\":\"Technical Report Qwen2.5-Coder Technical Report Binyuan Hui* Jian Yang*\",\"url\":\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2409.12186\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen2.5-LLM: Extending the boundary of LLMs | Qwen\",\"url\":\"https://qwenlm.github.io/blog/qwen2.5-llm/\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen2.5-LLM\",\"url\":\"https://qwen.ai/blog?id=qwen2.5-llm\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen2.5-Coder Series: Powerful, Diverse, Practical. | Qwen\",\"url\":\"https://qwenlm.github.io/blog/qwen2.5-coder-family/\"},{\"title\":\"Qwen AI for Coding: Reviews, Usage and Performance in 2026 | Second Talent\",\"url\":\"https://www.secondtalent.com/resources/qwen-ai-for-coding-reviews-usage-and-performance/\"},{\"title\":\"OpenCoder: The Open Cookbook for Top-Tier Code Large Language Models\",\"url\":\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2411.04905\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, I found information about the Qwen2.5-Coder technical report with official scores. Here's what I found:\n\n## Official Scores for Qwen2.5-Coder\n\n### HumanEval Performance\nThe Qwen2.5-Coder-7B achieves 88.4% on HumanEval, and the Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct records 37.6% Pass@1 on LiveCodeBench.\n\n### LiveCodeBench Performance\nLiveCodeBench measures the ability to handle the latest coding problems, and the Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct shows outstanding performance with 37.6% Pass@1.\n\n### Model Sizes and General Performance\nThe Qwen2.5-Coder-32B-Instruct model achieved the highest performance on EvalPlus, even outperforming DS-Coder-V2-Instruct, making it the most powerful open-source code model to date.\n\nThe Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct model demonstrated exceptional accuracy, significantly outperforming other models with a comparable parameter count and even surpassing larger models with over 20 billion parameters.\n\n### Overall Capabilities\nThe Qwen2.5-Coder instruct models achieve superior performance on benchmarks like HumanEval+ and LiveCodeBench, outperforming both similarly-sized and larger models in tasks such as code generation, reasoning, and editing.\n\nThe search results reference the official technical report but don't provide all specific score details for the 14B variant specifically. The official technical report is available on arXiv (2409.12186).\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"18dba446-077b-47f6-8015-b5b8230a0c1c","timestamp":"2026-06-21T07:35:07.308Z","toolUseResult":{"query":"Qwen2.5-Coder technical report HumanEval LiveCodeBench 7B 14B 32B official scores","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_014oLHiXSk8SNC8jRyhqkSWZ","content":[{"title":"Qwen2.5-Coder Technical Report","url":"https://www.emergentmind.com/papers/2409.12186"},{"title":"Qwen2.5-Coder Technical Report","url":"https://arxiv.org/html/2409.12186v3"},{"title":"Qwen2.5-Coder] LLM specialized for code generation, completion, and mathematical reasoning tasks | AI-SCHOLAR | AI: (Artificial Intelligence) Articles and technical information media","url":"https://ai-scholar.tech/en/articles/large-language-models/Qwen2.5-Coder"},{"title":"Technical Report Qwen2.5-Coder Technical Repo